{"tid":1631122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正字正確]以武制暴、示威者、五大訴求，而唔係私了、曱甴、六大訴求","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:09:34.000Z","uid":31511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a78cc3e3d151c9faf1a67f395227546efd424b8","tid":1631122,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"對外對內都係，唔好用錯字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.前線咁型幫大家[rmed]用合適既武力以武制暴[/red],唔好再用私了兩個字，都唔好貪好玩用鰤字，用得愈多對外觀感愈差。要灌輸以武制暴代替鰤字<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.唔好習慣暴徒，曱甴等稱呼，<span style=\"color: red;\">自嘲都唔得</span><br />\n要堅持用文宣說明兩個名稱都係有問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 就算係要解散警隊，都仲係叫<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span>,都係追究緊警方濫暴， 唔洗特登改口叫六大訴求咁多餘，正如撤回後都唔會改口叫四大訴求。"},{"pid":"f0669a2a7372d52783d3198846b109124c694dd1","tid":1631122,"uid":305321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"召喚師入，神獸要進化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631046\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631046</a>"},{"pid":"f77ab3934ee64d6be6b84ffec7544e91be5e210f","tid":1631122,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:48.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1aa03dd2f8095fefb8a5f3b16a298ba51ec08d8a","tid":1631122,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:49:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a05b5d1740b1aafa61f02ee90b33e50beb2e8139","tid":1631122,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47b405b992a5446f585b0ef752a7f49b1ac8d722","tid":1631122,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited